A tree stump is a type of scenery left on the ground when the dark variant of jungle tree in the dense Kharazi Jungle has been chopped down. After the jungle tree is chopped down, the player will automatically walk across the stump. The stump can otherwise not be walked across, and further movement requires chopping another jungle tree.

A stump will respawn into a jungle tree after a short amount of time. The tree stump has no interaction options.

A instance of the tree stump can also be found on an inaccessible island east of Fossil Island.

A '''tree stump''' is a type of scenery left on the ground when the dark variant of [[Jungle Tree (dense Kharazi Jungle)#Dark|jungle tree]] in the dense [[Kharazi Jungle]] has been chopped down. After the jungle tree is chopped down, the player will automatically walk across the stump. The stump can otherwise not be walked across, and further movement requires chopping another jungle tree.

A stump will respawn into a jungle tree after a short amount of time. The tree stump has no interaction options.

A instance of the tree stump can also be found on an inaccessible island east of [[Fossil Island]].
